# Hartmann Heat Pump ESPHome Integration

ðŸ‡µðŸ‡± **[Wersja polska dostÄ™pna](NOTICE_PL)**

This project provides an ESPHome integration for Hartmann heat pumps, based on the excellent [ESPHome Deye Inverter](https://github.com/Lewa-Reka/esphome-deye-inverter) project.

This project uses ESPHome and related components. Please refer to the NOTICE file for additional license information.

## Third-Party Components

- **ESPHome**: [https://esphome.io/](https://esphome.io/) - MIT License
- **Arduino ESP32**: [https://github.com/espressif/arduino-esp32](https://github.com/espressif/arduino-esp32) - LGPL 2.1 License
- **Home Assistant**: [https://www.home-assistant.io/](https://www.home-assistant.io/) - Apache 2.0 License

## Inspiration and Acknowledgments

This project is inspired by and based on:
- **Lewa-Reka** for the [ESPHome Deye Inverter](https://github.com/Lewa-Reka/esphome-deye-inverter) - Configuration structure and patterns
- [ESPHome Team](https://esphome.io/) - Home automation platform
- [Home Assistant Community](https://community.home-assistant.io/) - Continuous support and inspiration

